snippet.title: World Map Quiz - training mode
snippet.description:
World Map Quiz - training mode:
*play without time pressure
*making mistakes is allowed in that mode
*try many times to find correct answer
*eventually you can show the right answer
*training mode is available for all categories (flags, rivers, etc.)

How to download the app?

Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.qbis.guessthecountry

App Store:
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/world-map-quiz-qbis-studio/id1338262626
